      <title><![CDATA[Advertisement for Sale of Newly Arrived Africans, Charleston, July 24, 1769 [Advertisement]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/148</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
